Class Manipulation

  • java.lang.Object
    • hibernate.entities.Manipulation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    @Entity
public class Manipulation
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This entity class represents the comments posted on a resource. This has a many-to-one association from Resource entity. This has a composite primary key (mid,rid)
